#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/3.27/guides/datasource.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Datasource health check"
msgstr "数据源健康检查"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/datasource.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If you use the link:https://quarkus.io/extensions/io.quarkus/quarkus-smallrye-health[`quarkus-smallrye-health`] extension, the `quarkus-agroal` and reactive client extensions automatically add a readiness health check to validate the datasource."
msgstr "如果您使用了 link:https://quarkus.io/extensions/io.quarkus/quarkus-smallrye-health[quarkus-smallrye-health] 扩展 `，quarkus-agroal` 和 reactive client 扩展会自动添加一个就绪性健康检查，以验证数据源。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/datasource.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"When you access your application’s health readiness endpoint, `/q/health/ready` by default, you receive information about the datasource validation status.\n"
"If you have multiple datasources, all datasources are checked, and if a single datasource validation failure occurs, the status changes to `DOWN`."
msgstr "当您访问应用程序的健康状态就绪端点（默认地址为 `/q/health/ready` ）时，会收到有关数据源验证状态的信息。如果您有多个数据源，系统会检查所有数据源；如果其中任何一个数据源验证失败，状态将变为 `DOWN` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/datasource.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This behavior can be disabled by using the `quarkus.datasource.health.enabled` property."
msgstr "可以使用 `quarkus.datasource.health.enabled` 属性禁用该行为。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/datasource.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "To exclude only a particular datasource from the health check:"
msgstr "若要仅将特定数据源从健康检查中排除："

#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/3.27/guides/datasource.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Datasource metrics"
msgstr "数据源指标"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/datasource.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If you are using the xref:telemetry-micrometer.adoc[`quarkus-micrometer`] or xref:smallrye-metrics.adoc[`quarkus-smallrye-metrics`] extension, `quarkus-agroal` can contribute some datasource-related metrics to the metric registry.\n"
"This can be activated by setting the `quarkus.datasource.metrics.enabled` property to `true`."
msgstr "如果您使用 xref:telemetry-micrometer.adoc[quarkus-micrometer] 或 xref:smallrye-metrics.adoc[quarkus-smallrye-metrics] 扩展， `quarkus-agroal` 可以向度量注册表贡献一些数据源相关度量。可以通过将 `quarkus.datasource.metrics.enabled` 属性设置为 `true` 来激活该功能。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/datasource.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"For the exposed metrics to contain any actual values, a metric collection must be enabled internally by the Agroal mechanisms.\n"
"By default, this metric collection mechanism is enabled for all datasources when a metrics extension is present, and metrics for the Agroal extension are enabled."
msgstr "要使暴露的度量值包含任何实际值，Agroal 机制必须在内部启用度量集合。默认情况下，当有度量扩展时，所有数据源都会启用这种度量收集机制，并且 Agroal 扩展的度量也会启用。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/datasource.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"To disable metrics for a particular datasource, set `quarkus.datasource.jdbc.enable-metrics` to `false`, or apply `quarkus.datasource.<datasource name>.jdbc.enable-metrics` for a named datasource.\n"
"This disables collecting the metrics and exposing them in the `/q/metrics` endpoint if the mechanism to collect them is disabled."
msgstr "要禁用特定数据源的度量指标，请将 `quarkus.datasource.jdbc.enable-metrics` 设置为 `false` ，或对已命名的数据源应用 `quarkus.datasource.<datasource name>.jdbc.enable-metrics` 。如果收集度量指标的机制已禁用，则将禁用收集度量指标并在 `/q/metrics` 端点中公开这些指标。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/datasource.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Conversely, setting `quarkus.datasource.jdbc.enable-metrics` to `true`, or `quarkus.datasource.<datasource name>.jdbc.enable-metrics` for a named datasource explicitly enables metrics collection even if a metrics extension is not in use.\n"
"This can be useful if you need to access the collected metrics programmatically.\n"
"They are available after calling `dataSource.getMetrics()` on an injected `AgroalDataSource` instance."
msgstr "相反，如果将 `quarkus.datasource.jdbc.enable-metrics` 设置为 `true` ，或将 `quarkus.datasource.<datasource name>.jdbc.enable-metrics` 设置为已命名数据源，则即使未使用度量扩展，也可显式启用度量收集功能。如果需要以编程方式访问收集到的度量值，这将非常有用。在注入的 `AgroalDataSource` 实例上调用 `dataSource.getMetrics()` 后，就可以使用这些指标。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/datasource.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If the metrics collection for this datasource is disabled, all values result in zero."
msgstr "如果禁用了该数据源的度量值收集，则所有值均为零。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/3.27/guides/datasource.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Datasource tracing"
